author: Eric Branch
title: 49ers 25, Ravens 20: Niners pick on ex-teammate to pick up second win
text:
Photo: Scott Strazzante, The Chronicle San Francisco 49ers' Anquan Boldin and Colin Kaepernick celebrate Torrey Smith's 76-yard touchdown reception in 2nd quarter as Baltimore Ravens' Shareece Wright walks away during Niners' 25-20 win in NFL game at Levi's Stadium in Santa Clara, Calif., on Sunday, October 18, 2015. San Francisco 49ers' Anquan Boldin and Colin Kaepernick celebrate...
As unhappy as Shareece Wright was about not playing for the 49ers this season, some of his ex-teammates were equally pleased to see the cornerback on the field for the Ravens on Sunday.
